rComments: He is One of the premiere Professors of Voice in all of Canada!

Had him for an optional lesson this semester at Memorial.  He is hilarious! Great attitude and expects a lot,which is good.  Despite your year or level of singing, he is honest and challenges you to go beyond your comfort zone.
He really cracks the whip, and while it's good sometimes its too much to handle
Dr. Darryl is amazing! He's very hard to impress, so a compliment from him means a lot.
